\newcommand*{\TestDo}[2]{%
  \ifcase\numexpr#2\relax
  \else
    \edef\temp{\intcalcMod{#1}{#2}}%
    \Expect*{%
      \the\numexpr
      \intcalcMul{%
        \intcalcDiv{\intcalcAbs{#1}}{\intcalcAbs{#2}}%
      }{\intcalcAbs{#2}}%
      +\intcalcMod{\intcalcAbs{#1}}{\intcalcAbs{#2}}\relax
    }*{\the\numexpr\intcalcAbs{#1}\relax}%
  \fi
}
